714
00:42:15,470 --> 00:42:18,740
♪So deep, so boundless♪

715
00:42:19,080 --> 00:42:22,250
♪Just like your arms♪

716
00:42:22,740 --> 00:42:25,860
♪Shielding me from the dark clouds♪

717
00:42:26,150 --> 00:42:29,790
♪Always bearing it all in silence♪

718
00:42:29,790 --> 00:42:36,210
♪Even the long, long road gives me peace
when you're there♪

719
00:42:36,710 --> 00:42:41,110
♪Not one to show romance
in front of others♪

720
00:42:41,570 --> 00:42:44,660
♪You speak of dreams
with such calm simplicity♪

721
00:42:45,450 --> 00:42:50,250
♪But I know your heart
holds much deeper hopes♪

722
00:42:52,520 --> 00:42:54,360
♪I truly understand♪

723
00:42:54,850 --> 00:42:59,040
♪You speak of love so slowly♪

724
00:42:59,290 --> 00:43:05,260
♪But your eyes have already
told me everything♪

725
00:43:05,766 --> 00:43:08,456
♪Using up all my fortune♪

726
00:43:08,460 --> 00:43:12,860
♪Just to trade a lifetime with you♪

727
00:43:12,950 --> 00:43:15,170
♪Thank you for awakening♪

728
00:43:15,180 --> 00:43:20,260
♪The courage once hidden in my fear♪

729
00:43:20,400 --> 00:43:23,590
♪Turning every chance into certainty♪

730
00:43:23,920 --> 00:43:27,450
♪Turning every tie into companionship♪

731
00:43:27,530 --> 00:43:32,500
♪Blooming into brilliance
for all the years to come♪

732
00:43:32,500 --> 00:43:36,490
♪No one can tear us apart♪

733
00:43:36,680 --> 00:43:40,030
♪Each time my palm feels warmth again♪

734
00:43:40,290 --> 00:43:45,630
♪The memories return,
and I'm no longer alone♪

735
00:43:46,520 --> 00:43:50,510
♪No matter how far
across time and space♪

736
00:43:50,760 --> 00:43:54,160
♪My longing reaches you in silence♪

737
00:43:54,280 --> 00:43:58,810
♪No need to call out loudly♪

738
00:43:58,810 --> 00:44:01,480
♪No matter how much it takes♪

739
00:44:01,500 --> 00:44:05,910
♪To bring this drifting heart to shore♪

740
00:44:05,910 --> 00:44:09,170
♪Thank you for standing behind me♪

741
00:44:09,190 --> 00:44:13,240
♪Lighting up the darkness and despair♪

742
00:44:13,240 --> 00:44:16,710
♪The bigger the world,
the lonelier it feels♪

743
00:44:16,710 --> 00:44:20,480
♪Only by your side♪

744
00:44:20,490 --> 00:44:27,570
♪Can I truly feel this warmth inside♪
